<div id="main_content">
	<h2>UCF Police Hold High-Tech Training Exercise for Active Shooter Scenarios</h2>
	
	<p class="article_info">
		
			By Chad Binette
		
		<span class="date">April 14, 2008</span></p>
	
	
	
		<div class="article_img" style="width: 261px;">

			<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="../resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/1000/NE1421/en_US/officercrop.jpg" height="196" width="261"  /> 
			
				<p class="photo_credit">Photo: Jacque Brund</p>
			
			<p>UCF police officers entered a vacant building in teams of four in an effort to find and kill the "shooter" during Monday's training exercise. This scenario featured officers Jennifer Powers, Matthew Ahearn and Wilfredo Sotomayor.</p>
			
				<p class="note"><a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=00240041053a63cf501194e1a448c03701">Full Photo</a></p>
			
			
			
			
					
						
						
							
								<h3>Story Images</h3>
								<ul id="story_images">
							
						<li>
